Angry Birds game made using OPENGL

Controls:
A : Increase Cannon Angle
B : Reduce Cannon Angle
F : Increase Cannon Power
S : Decrease Cannon Power
UP : Zoom in
DOWN : Zoom Out
LEFT ; Pan-left
RIGHT : Pan-right
R : Reload Weapon
SPACE : Shoot

Mouse:
Left Click Hold & Drag : Change Cannon Angle
Right Click Hold & Drag : Horizontal Pan
Scroll In/Out : Zoom 
